Class PriorityQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • PriorityQueue

  • public class PriorityQueue
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to implement a priority queue. The states with the higher population have the higher priority.
    Version:
    1.0, 06/14/2019
    Author:
